 Thomas-Symonds]] {{small|MP FRHistS}}'''\n|-\n| style=\"width: 450px;\" |Shadow Minister of State for Crime Reduction and Courts\n| style=\"width: 320px;\" |[[Bambos Charalambous]] {{small|MP}}\n|-\n| style=\"width: 450px;\" |Shadow Minister of State for Policing and the Fire Service\n|[[Sarah Jones (politician)|Sarah Jones]] {{small|MP}}\n|-\n|Shadow Minister of State for Immigration\n|[[Holly Lynch]] {{small|MP}}\n|-\n|Shadow Minister of State for Security\n|[[Conor McGinn]] {{small|MP}}\n|-\n|Shadow Minister of State for Domestic Violence and Safeguarding\n|[[Jess Phillips]] {{small|MP}}\n|}\n\n=== Housing, Communities and Local Government ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" style=\"width: 1px; background: {{House of Commons/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"width: 450px;\" |[[Shadow Secretary of State for Communities and Local Government|'''Shadow Secretary of State for Communities and Local Government''']]\n| style=\"width: 320px;\" |'''[[Steve Reed (politician)|Steve Reed]] {{small|MP OBE}}'''\n|-\n| style=\"width: 450px;\" |[[Shadow Secretary of State for Housing|'''Shadow Secretary of State for Housing''']]\n| style=\"width: 320px;\" |'''[[Thangam Debbonaire]] {{small|MP}}'''\n|-\n| style=\"width: 450px;\" |Shadow Minister of State for Housing and Planning\n|[[Mike Amesbury]] {{small|MP}}\n|-\n|Shadow Minister of State for Faiths\n|[[Janet Daby]] {{small|MP}}\n|-\n|Shadow Minister of State for Local Government\n|[[Kate Hollern]] {{small|MP}}\n|-\n|Shadow Minister of State for Community Cohesion\n|[[Naz Shah]] {{small|MP}}\n|}\n\n=== International Development ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"width: 1px; background: {{House of Commons/meta/color}};\" |\n| style=\"width: 450px;\" |[[Shadow Secretary of State for International Development|'''Shadow Secretary of State for International Development''']]\n| style=\"width: 320px;\" |'''[[Preet Gill]] {{small|MP}}'''\n|-\n| style=\"width: 450px;\" |Shadow Minister of State for Interna